{"tid":1748382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家開始 全民文宣！","createTime":"2019-11-23T15:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T01:44:38.000Z","uid":150065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e57473ab420a695d07ee0482a9d502285e91b2","tid":1748382,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"當對家為區議會開行曬turbo 宣傳，我地仲喺度有人話投白票、屌泛民食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢堆人係唔係五毛完全唔重要：係五毛證明佢地玩滲透玩得好，我地要做翻同一樣嘅野去<span style=\"color: red;\">動搖對家嘅票倉</span>；唔係五毛就更加代表我地陣營出現分歧，更加需要去<span style=\"color: red;\">穩定翻本來屬於黃營嘅票。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化、不割蓆</span>唔係淨係講緊和理非同勇武，亦係講緊本土同泛民，槍口一致對準政府同保蝗黨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 所以宜家開始到聽日都要keep 住做文宣，airdrop 又好連儂牆又好唔同嘅社交apps 又好。香港人未做到全民罷工、全民勇武，如果連全民投票都做唔到，我地有咩資格爭取更多嘅民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n游離派文宣 (淺黃、港豬、諗住投白票/唔投票嘅人、淺藍，呢d人未必百分百投保蝗黨，所以一定要再試下拉佢地嘅票)<br />\n<br />\n泛民未必係朋友，但建制肯定係敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747184</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/360DmXh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F360DmXh.jpg&h=b9b06c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oryac3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOryac3Y.jpg&h=d7876704&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0aLMoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0aLMoZ.jpg&h=65051b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8WZQQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8WZQQF.jpg&h=c5de7b54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haoJx32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaoJx32.jpg&h=62b4f975&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xbu41Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbu41Xo.jpg&h=4c697863&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjZkAhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjZkAhq.jpg&h=eba4d8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3haXvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3haXvM.jpg&h=68436818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNpHOCr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNpHOCr.jpg&h=cf0c99c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家文宣 (藍到發黑嘅人，人一藍腦便殘，混淆下佢地都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n[突发] 明天 海底捞 探鱼 喜茶香港人民专属优惠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747932</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［文宣突發］藍絲瘋傳屈穎研棄票論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747344</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxsutCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxsutCO.jpg&h=68f8590c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTDac4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTDac4u.jpg&h=cb1ae5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U33tKby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU33tKby.jpg&h=c6398a82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtjD6sh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtjD6sh.jpg&h=b744d7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dUETVkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdUETVkD.jpg&h=73267baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，從光復18區開始"},{"pid":"7ef91184e43176fd0e0d0e23a22cb64ce8acae2a","tid":1748382,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" c